# DIX VISION Custom Avatar Placeholder

This directory is reserved for a custom DIX VISION Live2D avatar.

To add a custom avatar:
1. Create your Live2D model using Cubism Editor
2. Export the model files (moc3, json, textures, motions)
3. Place them in this directory
4. Update the model path in src/components/Live2DCanvas.tsx

See LIVE2D_CUSTOMIZATION_GUIDE.md for detailed instructions.
